{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1135,"text":"Everyone is both a learner"},{"time":3111,"text":"and a teacher."},{"time":4623,"text":"This is me being inspired"},{"time":7079,"text":"by my first tutor,"},{"time":8270,"text":"my mom,"},{"time":9215,"text":"and this is me teaching"},{"time":11838,"text":"Introduction to Artificial Intelligence"},{"time":13791,"text":"to 200 students"},{"time":15031,"text":"at Stanford University."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16303,"text":"Now the students and I"},{"time":17759,"text":"enjoyed the class,"},{"time":18935,"text":"but it occurred to me"},{"time":20351,"text":"that while the subject matter"},{"time":22062,"text":"of the class is advanced"},{"time":23351,"text":"and modern,"},{"time":24039,"text":"the teaching technology isn't."},{"time":26358,"text":"In fact, I use basically"},{"time":28694,"text":"the same technology as"},{"time":31064,"text":"this 14th-century classroom."},{"time":33694,"text":"Note the textbook,"},{"time":36494,"text":"the sage on the stage,"},{"time":39438,"text":"and the sleeping guy"},{"time":41337,"text":"in the back. (Laughter)"},{"time":42238,"text":"Just like today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45175,"text":"So my co-teacher,"},{"time":48286,"text":"Sebastian Thrun, and I thought,"},{"time":49926,"text":"there must be a better way."},{"time":51700,"text":"We challenged ourselves"},{"time":53354,"text":"to create an online class"},{"time":54645,"text":"that would be equal or better"},{"time":56276,"text":"in quality to our Stanford class,"},{"time":58612,"text":"but to bring it to anyone"},{"time":60822,"text":"in the world for free."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62452,"text":"We announced the class on July 29th,"},{"time":65020,"text":"and within two weeks, 50,000 people"},{"time":68229,"text":"had signed up for it."},{"time":69636,"text":"And that grew to 160,000 students"},{"time":72741,"text":"from 209 countries."},{"time":74805,"text":"We were thrilled to have"},{"time":76613,"text":"that kind of audience,"},{"time":77734,"text":"and just a bit terrified that we"},{"time":80373,"text":"hadn't finished preparing the class yet. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":82684,"text":"So we got to work."},{"time":84296,"text":"We studied what others had done,"},{"time":85932,"text":"what we could copy and what we could change."},{"time":88255,"text":"Benjamin Bloom had showed"},{"time":90916,"text":"that one-on-one tutoring works best,"},{"time":92725,"text":"so that's what we tried to emulate,"},{"time":94853,"text":"like with me and my mom,"},{"time":96293,"text":"even though we knew"},{"time":97798,"text":"it would be one-on-thousands."},{"time":99716,"text":"Here, an overhead video camera"},{"time":101917,"text":"is recording me as I'm talking"},{"time":103749,"text":"and drawing on a piece of paper."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105428,"text":"A student said, \"This class felt"},{"time":107837,"text":"like sitting in a bar"},{"time":108989,"text":"with a really smart friend"},{"time":110468,"text":"who's explaining something"},{"time":111672,"text":"you haven't grasped, but are about to.\""},{"time":113973,"text":"And that's exactly what we were aiming for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116089,"text":"Now, from Khan Academy, we saw"},{"time":118877,"text":"that short 10-minute videos"},{"time":120701,"text":"worked much better than trying"},{"time":122477,"text":"to record an hour-long lecture"},{"time":124548,"text":"and put it on the small-format screen."},{"time":126965,"text":"We decided to go even shorter"},{"time":129157,"text":"and more interactive."},{"time":130805,"text":"Our typical video is two minutes,"},{"time":133052,"text":"sometimes shorter, never more"},{"time":134804,"text":"than six, and then we pause for"},{"time":137493,"text":"a quiz question, to make it"},{"time":138860,"text":"feel like one-on-one tutoring."},{"time":140738,"text":"Here, I'm explaining how a computer uses"},{"time":143140,"text":"the grammar of English"},{"time":144388,"text":"to parse sentences, and here,"},{"time":146565,"text":"there's a pause and the student"},{"time":148629,"text":"has to reflect, understand what's going on"},{"time":150866,"text":"and check the right boxes"},{"time":152506,"text":"before they can continue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153923,"text":"Students learn best when"},{"time":156371,"text":"they're actively practicing."},{"time":157619,"text":"We wanted to engage them, to have them grapple"},{"time":159915,"text":"with ambiguity and guide them to synthesize"},{"time":162883,"text":"the key ideas themselves."},{"time":164548,"text":"We mostly avoid questions"},{"time":166260,"text":"like, \"Here's a formula, now"},{"time":167971,"text":"tell me the value of Y"},{"time":169046,"text":"when X is equal to two.\""},{"time":170258,"text":"We preferred open-ended questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172075,"text":"One student wrote, \"Now I'm seeing"},{"time":175253,"text":"Bayes networks and examples of"},{"time":177115,"text":"game theory everywhere I look.\""},{"time":178683,"text":"And I like that kind of response."},{"time":180421,"text":"That's just what we were going for."},{"time":182227,"text":"We didn't want students to memorize the formulas;"},{"time":184421,"text":"we wanted to change the way"},{"time":185611,"text":"they looked at the world."},{"time":186701,"text":"And we succeeded."},{"time":188027,"text":"Or, I should say, the students succeeded."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190427,"text":"And it's a little bit ironic"},{"time":192346,"text":"that we set about to disrupt traditional education,"},{"time":195259,"text":"and in doing so, we ended up"},{"time":197275,"text":"making our online class"},{"time":198859,"text":"much more like a traditional college class"},{"time":201186,"text":"than other online classes."},{"time":203027,"text":"Most online classes, the videos are always available."},{"time":206242,"text":"You can watch them any time you want."},{"time":208059,"text":"But if you can do it any time,"},{"time":210346,"text":"that means you can do it tomorrow,"},{"time":211851,"text":"and if you can do it tomorrow,"},{"time":213259,"text":"well, you may not ever"},{"time":215421,"text":"get around to it. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217179,"text":"So we brought back the innovation"},{"time":219371,"text":"of having due dates. (Laughter)"},{"time":221458,"text":"You could watch the videos"},{"time":222770,"text":"any time you wanted during the week,"},{"time":224682,"text":"but at the end of the week,"},{"time":225837,"text":"you had to get the homework done."},{"time":227554,"text":"This motivated the students to keep going, and it also"},{"time":229467,"text":"meant that everybody was working"},{"time":232323,"text":"on the same thing at the same time,"},{"time":233841,"text":"so if you went into a discussion forum,"},{"time":235338,"text":"you could get an answer from a peer within minutes."},{"time":238042,"text":"Now, I'll show you some of the forums, most of which"},{"time":240981,"text":"were self-organized by the students themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243747,"text":"From Daphne Koller and Andrew Ng, we learned"},{"time":246971,"text":"the concept of \"flipping\" the classroom."},{"time":248967,"text":"Students watched the videos"},{"time":250262,"text":"on their own, and then they"},{"time":251850,"text":"come together to discuss them."},{"time":253560,"text":"From Eric Mazur, I learned about peer instruction,"},{"time":256717,"text":"that peers can be the best teachers,"},{"time":259341,"text":"because they're the ones"},{"time":260773,"text":"that remember what it's like to not understand."},{"time":263621,"text":"Sebastian and I have forgotten some of that."},{"time":266302,"text":"Of course, we couldn't have"},{"time":268701,"text":"a classroom discussion with"},{"time":270333,"text":"tens of thousands of students,"},{"time":271879,"text":"so we encouraged and nurtured these online forums."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275365,"text":"And finally, from Teach For America,"},{"time":278413,"text":"I learned that a class is not"},{"time":279894,"text":"primarily about information."},{"time":281390,"text":"More important is motivation and determination."},{"time":284221,"text":"It was crucial that the students see"},{"time":286061,"text":"that we're working hard for them and"},{"time":287861,"text":"they're all supporting each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289270,"text":"Now, the class ran 10 weeks,"},{"time":292238,"text":"and in the end, about half of the 160,000 students watched"},{"time":296149,"text":"at least one video each week,"},{"time":297712,"text":"and over 20,000 finished all the homework,"},{"time":300405,"text":"putting in 50 to 100 hours."},{"time":302069,"text":"They got this statement of accomplishment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303622,"text":"So what have we learned?"},{"time":305741,"text":"Well, we tried some old ideas"},{"time":308557,"text":"and some new and put them together,"},{"time":310214,"text":"but there are more ideas to try."},{"time":312296,"text":"Sebastian's teaching another class now."},{"time":314110,"text":"I'll do one in the fall."},{"time":315478,"text":"Stanford Coursera, Udacity, MITx"},{"time":319238,"text":"and others have more classes coming."},{"time":321509,"text":"It's a really exciting time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322997,"text":"But to me, the most exciting"},{"time":324469,"text":"part of it is the data that we're gathering."},{"time":327445,"text":"We're gathering thousands"},{"time":330141,"text":"of interactions per student per class,"},{"time":331797,"text":"billions of interactions altogether,"},{"time":334005,"text":"and now we can start analyzing that,"},{"time":336509,"text":"and when we learn from that,"},{"time":337973,"text":"do experimentations,"},{"time":339214,"text":"that's when the real revolution will come."},{"time":341454,"text":"And you'll be able to see the results from"},{"time":344230,"text":"a new generation of amazing students."},{"time":346493,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}